Author: Kruti <kpendharkar@vmware.com>
Date:   Mon Feb 19 06:32:44 2024 -0800

    Fix out-of-bound access issues reported by Coverity
    
    Do not pass PATH_MAX and FILENAME_MAX to Str_Strlen function call.

