     * Flatcar Container Linux, all releases
     * Rocky 8 and later releases
     * AlmaLinux OS 8 and later releases
    
    Addresses:
      https://github.com/vmware/open-vm-tools/pull/573
      https://github.com/vmware/open-vm-tools/pull/513

