commit 54d0128fc4ec2f2b256b88ad978b780c696b9c5d
Author: John Wolfe <jwolfe@vmware.com>
Date:   Tue Dec 22 12:22:03 2020 -0800

    Corrected a few typos and reworded sentences in tools.conf.
    
